121
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:02,780
(A noble spirit admired by all,
gone too soon to the grief of friends)

122
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,040
Zekai.

123
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,960
Is it lonely inside?

124
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,160
Cold?

125
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:25,220
(A noble spirit admired by all,
gone too soon to the grief of friends)

126
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:35,660
(A noble spirit admired by all,
gone too soon to the grief of friends)

127
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,080
Don't be afraid.

128
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,880
Once this is all over,

129
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,120
we'll see each other again soon.

130
00:10:04,780 --> 00:10:12,180
♪As dusk approaches, dreams unfold♪

131
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:19,220
♪Laughter drifts with the wind,
hard to hold♪

132
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:23,100
♪Entwined within the mortal world♪

133
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:26,620
♪Watching fates intertwine, unfurled♪

134
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:33,780
♪Like moths chasing flames,
to blaze they're drawn♪

135
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:37,980
♪We brave the darkness,
spiraling into cocoons♪

136
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:41,500
♪Chasing a single, unwavering dream♪

137
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:45,260
♪But life's endless twists and turns
can't be undone♪

138
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:48,980
♪As fleeting splendor fades
without regret♪

139
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:52,860
♪We cross the smoke and ashes,
torn by goodbyes♪

140
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:56,180
♪In every moment♪

141
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:59,940
♪Stained by the verses of dawn's light♪

142
